-- South African Judge Joffe Says There Is Proof Jackie Selebi Took Money
-- Franz Wild
-- 2010-07-02T09:20:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-02/south-african-judge-joffe-says-there-is-proof-jackie-selebi-took-money.html

          
          
             South African Judge Meyer Joffe said
there is proof that former police chief Jackie Selebi took some
money inappropriately.  
 Joffe was speaking in Johannesburg in a ruling on a
corruption case against Selebi today.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Franz Wild in Johannesburg at 
 fwild@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        